清，指自己從來沒有在訪問中表達支持或反對任何政治人物或派別，又引用美國前總統甘迺迪的名言「Ask not what your country can do for you, ask what you can do for your country.」（不要問國家可以為你做什麼，你應該要問自己可以為國家做什麼），認為可「減少之後的誤會」"},{"pid":"89063062727b5baff364f1b46327bcf48fad2b5c","tid":896283,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1aa7a43a635f64ceeef51d0a59a489c34481167","tid":896283,"uid":76388,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:41:26.000Z","msg":"連登仔一早唔記得晒喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f53494b791838e4edf0fdfdf7a6df7bd28b51dc","tid":896283,"uid":11254,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"d1aa7a43a635f64ceeef51d0a59a489c34481167","tid":896283,"uid":76388,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:41:26.000Z","msg":"連登仔一早唔記得晒喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:42:49.000Z","msg":"00後個陣都未出世"},{"pid":"8bf7ba742cfdfa09bbd285e68e5672c385b315f4","tid":896283,"uid":129521,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:43:28.000Z","msg":"Gem咁可愛 前事不提了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1b3e1eca0dfe6d65afc072fc8e1ef0385f3959","tid":896283,"uid":76388,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:44:40.000Z","msg":"有時打開報紙，見到有人好激烈地反對某些事，或者從早到晚叫特首下台，我反而覺得：「嘩！使唔使呀？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我不覺得一個特首、或者一個政府可以怎樣幫助市民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2fd91ca918746e92649e05cfcf640bffd7cf14a","tid":896283,"uid":126769,"like":5,"dislike":21,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T01:44:54.000Z","msg":"人地已經去到nasa表演<br />\n你仲停緊係連登做鍵盤戰士"},{"pid":"dd340d832733230d9e2eee37ff27e9dcf0